# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UML→Java — Environment Variables Template
#
# This file is committed to version control with PLACEHOLDER values only.
# Copy it to .env.local and fill in your real credentials there.
# .env.local is gitignored (via *.local) so your secrets stay off GitHub.
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Supabase (Auth + Realtime collaboration) ────────────────────────────────
# Create a free project at https://supabase.com
# Settings → API → copy Project URL and anon public key
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key-here

# ── OpenAI (AI Import feature — optional) ───────────────────────────────────
# Required only if you want the "AI Import" diagram generation feature.
# Get a key at https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
VITE_OPENAI_KEY=sk-your-openai-key-here
